ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實捉到你！！！</blockquote><br />\n下 我唔知架 上網見到架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec199152ca549e0768056ce9bcb468692dfd33c1","tid":296534,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"實捉到你"},{"pid":"6de6d5075b38ca1eb0a95c0ace54e406242542a2","tid":296534,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"巧合姐<br />\n文字獄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20d17661f78427da6daffead91c1eea6646fd65","tid":296534,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0255b1cc39d07694d18cc1986804362dabee7b01","tid":296534,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樓主你又點睇呀<br />\n下下掉低個題目就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我咪覺得東方盡左傳媒監察政府同揭露時弊既責任，可以令我了解更多呢方面既資訊，有效增加個人時事見識，所以都係一份幾值得睇既報章"},{"pid":"8dfad7fb02c6b7f1fb59df7ecec1aa326de891c1","tid":296534,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實捉到你</blockquote><br />\n其實誣衊邊一份報章都係犯法同唔應該，就算你抹黑蘋果日報都一樣。點解要將呢種行為合理化？同你立場價值觀不一就要咁做？咁都幾膚淺下。人地又唔唔係散播劣質信息，叫你地去盲目支持政府。取向較為保守唔係罪黎，反正人地係揭發政府施政同管治失誤方面出左一大分力"},{"pid":"a361e8f4ef2af169a46c06ce5b56bd0217016306","tid":296534,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"766084b82e417e028f5053f6ddd0ebc68f69153c","tid":296534,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bff99ea070d084a8cb2ea5185ba5ccac6b386ea","tid":296534,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c83e554f169b86caa7c162ad9ea36540b4574d1","tid":296534,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:12:05.000Z","msg":"一百分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528754dd165ba329b5d11692373e467aeccdce63","tid":296534,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}